---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About VeltRex Esports | Moroccan Esports Organization" description="Learn about VeltRex Esports — our mission, teams, and vision for competitive gaming in Morocco.">

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-white/10 px-6 py-20 lg:px-12">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(134,36,229,0.22),transparent_38%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:46px_46px] opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="absolute -left-24 top-16 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[#8624E5]/10 blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-24 bottom-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-white/5 blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#8624E5]">About VeltRex</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading max-w-6xl text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.92] sm:text-7xl text-balance">Building Competitive Esports And Gaming Culture In Morocco</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-white/72 sm:text-lg">VeltRex Esports is a Moroccan esports organization built around competition, structure, and long term growth. VeltRex combines pro teams, community building, and strong execution to create one of the most ambitious gaming brands in Morocco.</p>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-5">
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/50 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]"><p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#8624E5]">Teams</p><p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black uppercase">4</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Active competitive rosters.</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/50 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]"><p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#8624E5]">Achievements</p><p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black uppercase">—</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Building our competitive record.</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/50 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]"><p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#8624E5]">Events</p><p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black uppercase">—</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Planning our first events.</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/50 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]"><p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#8624E5]">Players Reached</p><p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black uppercase">1514+</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Participants across organized events.</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/50 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]"><p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#8624E5]">Community</p><p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black uppercase">3.3K+</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Discord members and growing.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 py-16 lg:px-12">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
      <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-8 transition duration-300 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04]">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#8624E5]">Who We Are</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-black uppercase text-balance">A Modern Esports Brand</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-8 text-white/75">VeltRex is more than a team. It is a structured gaming brand built to connect competitive performance, community energy, and brand opportunities under one strong identity.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-white/75">With teams across multiple titles and a growing presence in the Moroccan gaming scene, VeltRex is positioned as both a competitive force and a media-driven esports brand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-8 transition duration-300 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:bg-white/[0.04]">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#8624E5]">Mission &amp; Goals</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-black uppercase text-balance">Where We Are Going</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-8 text-white/75">
          <li>🔹 Develop Moroccan esports talent and nurture emerging players.</li>
          <li>🔹 Build stronger competitive rosters across major titles.</li>
          <li>🔹 Grow VeltRex into one of the strongest gaming brands in Morocco.</li>
          <li>🔹 Create long term value for communities, players, and partners.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-6 py-16 lg:px-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#8624E5]">Social Proof</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-black uppercase sm:text-5xl text-balance">Presence, Reach, And Performance</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 text-center transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(134,36,229,0.10)]"><p class="text-5xl font-black text-white">31K+</p><p class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold text-white/85">Instagram Followers</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 text-center transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(134,36,229,0.10)]"><p class="text-5xl font-black text-white">3.3K+</p><p class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold text-white/85">Discord Members</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 text-center transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(134,36,229,0.10)]"><p class="text-5xl font-black text-white">4M+</p><p class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold text-white/85">Monthly Views</p></div>
        <div class="group border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 text-center transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/40 hover:shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(134,36,229,0.10)]"><p class="text-5xl font-black text-white">13-34</p><p class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold text-white/85">Core Audience Age</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3 items-stretch">
        <div class="h-full border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:border-[#8624E5]/35">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase">Competitive Side</h3>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 Active competitive teams across multiple titles.</li>
            <li>🔹 VeltRex also operates with an academy approach for player development.</li>
            <li>🔹 Our male and female Valorant teams are originally academy teams built to grow step by step.</li>
            <li>🔹 They have their own coach, structured practice sessions, and support in learning the basics of competitive play.</li>
            <li>🔹 The goal is not only to compete, but to teach players how to improve and become professional over time.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="h-full border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:border-[#8624E5]/35">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase">Community Side</h3>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 A growing Discord community around gaming and esports.</li>
            <li>🔹 An audience built through content, tournaments, and social media.</li>
            <li>🔹 Strong engagement with Gen Z and young gaming audiences.</li>
            <li>🔹 A brand identity designed to scale in both online and live spaces.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="h-full border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0B0C] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:border-[#8624E5]/35">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase">Brand Value</h3>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 Combines esports credibility with strong youth appeal.</li>
            <li>🔹 Built for partnerships, activations, and long term brand growth.</li>
            <li>🔹 Strong fit for gaming, tech, lifestyle, and youth-focused brands.</li>
            <li>🔹 Designed to grow as a modern Moroccan esports organization.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 py-16 lg:px-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#8624E5]">Team &amp; Leadership</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl font-black uppercase text-balance">The People Behind VeltRex</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="group flex h-full flex-col border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/45 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_26px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]">
          <div class="relative mb-5 overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
            <img src="/assets/images/ceo.jpeg" alt="Team member photo" class="h-[260px] w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase leading-tight">VeltRex Founder</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#8624E5]">Founder &amp; CEO</p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 Visionary leader driving the organization.</li>
            <li>🔹 2+ years in esports, organizing tournaments and events.</li>
            <li>🔹 Leading VeltRex vision, growth, and partnerships.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="group flex h-full flex-col border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/45 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_26px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]">
          <div class="relative mb-5 overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
            <img src="/assets/images/coo.png" alt="Team member photo" class="h-[260px] w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase leading-tight">VeltRex COO</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#8624E5]">Co-Founder &amp; COO</p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 Organized 10+ esports tournaments and online events.</li>
            <li>🔹 Built a creator network reaching 10M+ followers.</li>
            <li>🔹 Supports operations, structure, and execution.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="group flex h-full flex-col border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/45 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_26px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]">
          <div class="relative mb-5 overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
            <img src="/assets/images/cm.jpg" alt="Team member photo" class="h-[260px] w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase leading-tight">VeltRex CM</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#8624E5]">Community Manager</p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 Content creator since 2012.</li>
            <li>🔹 Active in esports and tournament organization since 2018.</li>
            <li>🔹 Recognized figure in the Moroccan gaming scene.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="group flex h-full flex-col border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[#8624E5]/45 hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:shadow-[0_0_26px_rgba(134,36,229,0.12)]">
          <div class="relative mb-5 overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
            <img src="/assets/images/team-mobile.jpg" alt="Team member photo" class="h-[260px] w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-black uppercase leading-tight">VeltRex Mobile</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#8624E5]">Mobile Manager</p>
          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75">
            <li>🔹 4+ years of experience managing multiple esports teams.</li>
            <li>🔹 2+ years organizing esports tournaments and events.</li>
            <li>🔹 Focused on roster development, performance, and team structure.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
